:: head_fs_head_ms_1
<<nobr>>
<<speech "thalara">>This potion‚Ä¶ doesn‚Äôt erase. It rebalances. But yes, she will step aside for now.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>She‚Äôs still there. I can almost see her outline, just behind my eyes.<</speech>><br>

