:: head_fm_head_fs_1
<<nobr>>
<<speech "thalara">>You know, most who walk forward through change rarely glance back. And fewer still ask to undo the spell‚Äôs embroidery.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>Maybe I just need to know what‚Äôs still mine. If anything is.<</speech>><br>

